{
  "uuid": "a5a6647dccc3ef8b659e6ea5f619897c",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "English Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the role</strong><br>\n<br>\nWe are seeking a secondary school level English Teacher to join our team at Ruisheng Education Centre (3 mins walk from Clarke Quay MRT). This is a full-time position that offers the opportunity to work with dedicated students and colleagues in a dynamic and supportive learning environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Delivering engaging and effective lessons in your subject area to secondary school students</li>\n  <li>Developing and implementing creative lesson plans that meet curriculum standards and cater to diverse learning needs</li>\n  <li>Assessing student progress, providing constructive feedback, and maintaining accurate records</li>\n  <li>Collaborating with fellow teachers to share best practices and continuously improve teaching methods</li>\n  <li>Participating in staff meetings, professional development activities, and other school initiatives</li>\n  <li>Fostering a positive and inclusive classroom culture that encourages student participation and growth</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's degree in English or a relevant subject area</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year of teaching experience at the secondary school level</li>\n  <li>Able to work both weekends 9am to 6pm and Mon to Wed 10am to 7pm (rest days on Thursday and Friday)</li>\n  <li>Strong subject matter expertise and a passion for teaching and learning</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to adapt teaching styles to meet the diverse needs of students</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Please send us your resume and state your current and expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About us</strong><br>\nRuisheng Education Centre is a leading provider of high-quality educational services in the Clarke Quay Area. Our mission is to empower students to reach their full potential through innovative and personalized learning experiences. With a team of dedicated and experienced educators, we are committed to creating a dynamic and supportive learning environment that inspires academic excellence and personal growth.</p>\n<p>If you are passionate about making a positive impact on the lives of young learners, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity. Click the \"Apply Now\" button to submit your application.</p>",
